<p>Chelsea: Mendy, Azpilicueta, Tomori, Zouma, Chilwell, Jorginho, Kovacic, Hudson-Odoi, Mount, Werner, Giroud.Subs: Arrizabalaga, Kante, Barkley, Abraham, James, Havertz, Emerson Palmieri.</p>

